==Most prominent summits==
{{GeoGroup|section=Most prominent summits}}
Of the most prominent summits of Utah, eight peaks are [[ultra-prominent summit]]s with more than {{convert|1500|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence and 33 peaks exceed {{convert|1000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence.
{{clear}}
