[[Category:Atmospheric boundaries]]

The [[Bayer designation]] '''Tau Serpentis''' (τ Ser / τ Serpentis) is shared by a collection of eight [[star]]s, '''τ<sup>1</sup> Serpentis''' through '''τ<sup>8</sup> Serpentis''', in the head of the [[constellation]] [[Serpens]]. They are distributed within a box of size 40 minutes in [[right ascension]] by 3.5° in [[declination]]. They are numbered by increasing right ascension: * [[Tau¹ Serpentis|Tau<sup>1</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 9 Serpentis or HD 137471. * [[Tau² Serpentis|Tau<sup>2</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 12 Serpentis or HD 138527. * [[Tau³ Serpentis|Tau<sup>3</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 15 Serpentis or HD 139074. * [[Tau4 Serpentis|Tau<sup>4</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 17 Serpentis or HD 139216. * [[Tau5 Serpentis|Tau<sup>5</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 18 Serpentis or HD 139225. * [[Tau6 Serpentis|Tau<sup>6</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 19 Serpentis or HD 140027. * [[Tau7 Serpentis|Tau<sup>7</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 22 Serpentis or HD 140232. * [[Tau8 Serpentis|Tau<sup>8</sup> Serpentis]], also designated 26 Serpentis or HD 140729.
